ğŸ”§ Development Features
Secure Expression Evaluation
Uses Python's Abstract Syntax Tree (AST) module to parse and evaluate expressions safely, preventing code injection attacks.

Memory Management
Browser-based LocalStorage keeps memory values persistent across sessions.

Error Handling
Graceful error messages without page reloads for better user experience.

